415
00:41:18.323 --> 00:41:19.365
[David groans]

416
00:41:22.869 --> 00:41:23.995
[grunting]

417
00:42:02.200 --> 00:42:03.242
[bone cracking]

418
00:42:15.713 --> 00:42:16.798
[grunting]

